api-1  | DEBUG [app.utils.layout_normalizer] ["Have you attended Young Technology Scholars Programme? Where did you hear about Plaksha University? Declaration Disclosure Have You Ever Had A First Information Report (FIR) Filed Against You Or Been Involved In Any Legal And/Or Criminal Proceeding? No Consent By submitting this admissions form, you acknowledge and consent to Plaksha University's data handling practices. Any personal information you provide, including academic records and contact details, will be stored internally, and may be shared with selected offices at Plaksha University for administrative and academic purposes. If you are applying for a scholarship, please note that your financial data and supporting documents may also be shared with key stakeholders involved in scholarship matters. All data will be handled with utmost confidentiality and in compliance with relevant data protection laws. I Agree Honour Pledge The information provided in this form is true to the best of my knowledge. I pledge that the entire application is a product of my effort and no part of it has been taken directly from other sources. If at any time during the course of the admissions process or later after joining the programme, the information provided by me is found to be false, untrue, or incorrect, then Plaksha University's Office of Admissions may exercise the right to rescind the offer of admissions made to me and nullify my enrollment during or after the programme, as applicable to me. Applicant Name:"]
